== 个人生活 ==
1972年，艾伦与[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]计算机科学教授和合作者[[Jacob_T._Schwartz|Jacob T. Schwartz]]结婚<ref name="oral-history"/>。 他们于1982年离婚<ref name="nytimes obit">{{cite web|last=Metz|first=Cade|date=August 8, 2020|title=Frances Allen, Who Helped Hardware Understand Software, Dies at 88|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/08/technology/frances-allen-dead.html|access-date=December 30, 2020|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]}}</ref>。

艾伦于2020年8月4日，即她88岁生日，死于[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]并发症<ref name="nytimes obit"/><ref name="wapost obit">{{cite news | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/frances-allen-first-woman-to-win-turing-award-for-contributions-to-computing-dies-at-88/2020/08/06/7ea7d7a2-d7f0-11ea-930e-d88518c57dcc_story.html | title=  Frances Allen, first woman to win Turing Award for contributions to computing, dies at 88 | first = Glenn | last=  Refkin  |date = August 7, 2020 | access-date = August 8, 2020 |newspaper = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Remembering Frances Allen|url=https://www.ibm.com/blogs/research/2020/08/remembering-frances-allen/|publisher=[[IBM|IBM]]|date=August 5, 2020}}</ref>。

